      "content": "it just feels like i'm living in a ghost house. i try to distract myself with work or stuff but then i come home and the emptiness just hits me all over again. i'm just so tired of the ache. it's like i can't even remember what it feels like to not be hurting. i just want it to stop. i want the pain to just stop.",
