      "content": "counselors and support lines dont really help when the feeling is this permanent. it's like... i've tried everything and the hole just stays there. i look at my life and i don't see a future, i just see more silence. sometimes i think the only way to actually find peace is to just stop fighting and let go of everything. does that even make sense? that there's just no point in trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken?",
